<i>noun</i>: 능지처참 [능지처참] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>능지처참 [능지처참]</dt><br>
<dd>quartering; hacking a criminal to pieces</dd><br>
<dd>(옛날에) 대역죄를 진 죄인의 머리, 몸통, 팔, 다리를 찢어 죽이는 형벌.</dd><br>
<dd>(archaic) A punishment for high treason, which tears the criminal's head, body, arms, and legs apart to death.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>